.TH wxSpinCtrl 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxSpinCtrl \- \fIwxSpinCtrl\fR combines \fIwxTextCtrl\fR and \fIwxSpinButton\fR in one control.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.SS "Styles"

.PP
This class supports the following styles:


.sp
